```

---

## 🎯 HOW IT ALL WORKS TOGETHER (The full story!)
```
User uploads a file
        ↓
🔐 Python makes a SHA-256 hash (magic fingerprint)
        ↓
🤖 AI module checks: Human or AI made this?
        ↓
⛓️ Smart contract saves hash + creator + time on Blockchain
        ↓
✅ Anyone can upload same file to VERIFY it's real!








# Install Node.js (go to nodejs.org and download it)
node --version   # check it worked

# Install Python
python --version

# Install these helpful packages
npm install ethers hardhat @openzeppelin/contracts
pip install flask web3 hashlib Pillow
```

**Also install:**
- **MetaMask** browser extension (your crypto wallet 👛)
- **VS Code** (where you write code 💻)

