### 📁 STEP 3: Set Up Your Project Folder
```
ProofOfOrigin/
│
├── blockchain/          ← Smart contract lives here
│   └── contracts/
│       └── ProofOfOrigin.sol
│
├── backend/             ← Python server lives here
│   └── app.py
│
├── frontend/            ← Website lives here
│   └── index.html
│
└── ai_module/           ← AI detector lives here
    └── detector.py


Image                          Result
Midjourney PNG🤖 AI — 99% — "AI tool signature: 
Midjourney"Stable Diffusion PNG🤖 AI — 98% — "SD prompt parameters found"
iPhone photo👤 Human — 92% — "Real camera: Apple iPhone"
Samsung photo👤 Human — 92% — "Real camera: Samsung Galaxy"
JPEG with no EXIF🤖 AI — 72% — "No EXIF data"
Downloaded PNG🤖 AI — 65% — "Empty metadata"









Case                         Result                            Why
AI image posted on WhatsApp           🤖 AI ~65%         WhatsApp strips EXIF — less evidence
Real photo edited in Photoshop        👤 Human ~75%      Camera EXIF still there
Real photo with all EXIF removed      🤖 AI ~72%         Looks suspicious — no EXIF
AI image watermarked & re-saved       🤖 AI ~65%         Metadata stripped but no camera
Screenshot of AI image                ⚠️ Uncertain 55%   Screenshot has no EXIF at all
PDF containing AI image               👤 Human 60%       Treated as binary — can't analyze inside